==English==
=== Intransitive verb ===
[[Category:Idioms]]
'''[[take]] [[the]] [[piss]]'''

#(''coarse UK slang'') to [[ridicule]] or [[mock]]
#*''Are you '''takin' the piss'''? You'll get yer 'ead bashed in.''
[[Category:Slang]]

====Usage notes====
*As this phrase may be found offensive, it is often [[bowdlerise]]d to '''[[take the pee]]''' or censored in print as '''take the p***''' or, less commonly, '''take the p&mdash;'''. A common jocular euphemism is "to extract the urine" (a formal equivalent of the literal meaning of the words).

